Design DB model for Guvi Zen class

1. Students
student_id (Primary Key)
first_name
last_name
email
phone_number
enrollment_date
status (active, graduated, etc.)
class_id (Foreign Key to Class)
2. Courses
course_id (Primary Key)
course_name
description
start_date
end_date
mentor_id (Foreign Key to Mentor)
total_chapters
3. Mentors
mentor_id (Primary Key)
first_name
last_name
email
phone_number
specialization
4. Classes
class_id (Primary Key)
class_name
course_id (Foreign Key to Courses)
start_date
end_date
5. Student Attendance
attendance_id (Primary Key)
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
class_id (Foreign Key to Classes)
date
status (Present, Absent)
6. Tasks
task_id (Primary Key)
task_name
description
assigned_date
due_date
course_id (Foreign Key to Courses)
class_id (Foreign Key to Classes)
7. Task Submissions
submission_id (Primary Key)
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
task_id (Foreign Key to Tasks)
submission_date
task_mark
status (Pending, Submitted, Graded)
8. Mock Assessments
assessment_id (Primary Key)
chapter_number
course_id (Foreign Key to Courses)
total_marks
9. Mock Test Results
test_result_id (Primary Key)
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
assessment_id (Foreign Key to Mock Assessments)
marks_obtained
date_of_test
10. Queries
query_id (Primary Key)
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
mentor_id (Foreign Key to Mentors)
query_text
query_date
status (Resolved, Unresolved)
11. Capstone Projects
project_id (Primary Key)
project_name
description
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
submission_date
mentor_feedback
12. Leave Applications
leave_id (Primary Key)
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
class_id (Foreign Key to Classes)
leave_start_date
leave_end_date
reason
status (Approved, Rejected, Pending)
13. Interview Tasks
interview_task_id (Primary Key)
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
task_description
task_assigned_date
task_due_date
task_status (Completed, Pending)
interview_round
14. Placement Board
placement_board_id (Primary Key)
company_name
job_role
placement_date
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
status (Selected, Rejected)
15. Final Placement Round
final_round_id (Primary Key)
student_id (Foreign Key to Students)
company_name
interview_date
result (Selected, Not Selected)
